data.description: Step inside this beautiful 3-bed, 2-bath home in the charming Pheasant Run neighborhood with a pool, solar, a newer water heater, and many modern updates. Heading through the front door, you will notice the updated LVP flooring throughout. The open living area comes with a gas fireplace, room for a breakfast table, and a large slider to access the backyard. The kitchen is equipped with tile countertops, white appliances, and a breakfast bar. Each bedroom features modern colors, spacious closets, and the master bedroom has a large walk-in closet. Both restrooms come with a tub/shower combo, as well as tile countertops. When entering the backyard oasis, you'll fall in love with the swimming pool, block wall fencing, pergola that provides covered seating, as well as spacious side yards.
